486
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:20,880
You're trouble.

487
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:26,560
It's you !

488
00:27:28,040 --> 00:27:29,720
How is that possible ? How ?

489
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:33,640
