493
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:49,560
I just can't imagine
how horrible this was for you.

494
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:51,280
It was nothing.

495
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:54,080
Coming back from the dead,
that's not hard.

496
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:55,520
You know what's hard ?

497
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:57,680
Getting from Syria
to Germany.

498
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:01,440
