501
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:10,440
If you make it to the border of Turkey,
they'll offer you an appointment

502
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:11,760
five years from now.

503
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:16,040
If you're lucky, you get to navigate
