507
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:26,120
- You'd slap 'em twice.
- Yeah.

508
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:30,880
There are some amazing people
coming through that border.

509
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:35,080
I read about this incredible 16-year-old
girl called Noujain Mustaffa.

510
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:39,040
- Noujain Mustaffa ?
- Yes, Noujain Mustaffa.

511
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:43,040
- She's our kind of people ?
- She's our kind of people.

512
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:47,320
Maybe you'll get
to meet her one day.

513
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:51,480
But right now, you are
not going anywhere, mister.

514
00:28:54,640 --> 00:29:00,200
If we can raise
EJ DiMera from the dead,

515
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:02,280
